{"tid":1063254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人間避雷針-張賢勝","createTime":"2019-03-15T15:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T15:47:00.000Z","uid":238483,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de81030ce0f37d57b59ec642174baf124cf9fbe5","tid":1063254,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"「頹廢美&rarr;陽光明朗」BEAST出身的張賢勝入伍前後，形象大轉變！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/114827#images-1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F114827%23images-1&h=03bf4f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友調侃張賢勝是人間避雷針，沒加入BIGBANG，離開了BEAST，完美躲過了這場災難性事件...<br />\n<br />\n近日因為「韓娛大地震」事件，不少明星都長期登在韓網熱搜中。 今日因為龍俊亨宣佈退出HIGHLIGHT，連帶了Beast、張賢勝等詞也上了熱搜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/114827#images-2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F114827%23images-2&h=110ae0b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/114827#images-3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F114827%23images-3&h=a9b687dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日有網友對比了張賢勝在入伍前後的形象轉變，入伍前以頹廢美著稱的張賢勝，標誌性的妝容是煙熏妝。 在去年7月入伍後的近況被公開，戴著鏡框眼鏡，面容朴素。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/114827#images-4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F114827%23images-4&h=3461bf64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/114827#images-5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F114827%23images-5&h=8cddd801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/114827#images-6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F114827%23images-6&h=9e6877ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對此網友評論：「在軍隊的樣子看起來舒服多了、臉色看起來亮多了啊、他就應該在軍隊裡過日子，有人樣了」等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白粉仔都有人吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}